  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 06/06/2018 1:40pm CT (18:40 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.15.2-ListViews\">List Views</h2><p>List views are now more condensed on smaller screen sizes by leveraging more text-wrapping within columns and dynamically resizing the actions column.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.15.2-Boldtextonticketnotes\">Bold text on ticket notes</h2><p>We have added a new font variation to support bolded text better.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.15.2-Checkboxclickableareaupdate\">Checkbox clickable area update</h2><p>The checkbox clickable area was too wide (full width of the container). Now the clickable area of a checkbox is just the checkbox, and sometimes the label as well.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.15.2-CatalogItemEdit-SaveButton\">Catalog Item Edit - Save Button\u00a0</h2><p>To improve usability, the save button will now &quot;stick&quot; to the top of the screen when you scroll past it so that it is always visible.</p>",
